{"tid":1426247,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"澳洲對港提高旅警 列高度警戒","createTime":"2019-08-07T01:33:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T01:36:06.000Z","uid":56881,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"46c360de312d0aeb2ad2923c91b2dea9431144fc","tid":1426247,"uid":56881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T01:33:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%BE%B3%E6%B4%B2%E5%B0%8D%E6%B8%AF%E6%8F%90%E9%AB%98%E6%97%85%E8%AD%A6-%E5%88%97%E9%AB%98%E5%BA%A6%E8%AD%A6%E6%88%92-214500103.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E6%25B4%25B2%25E5%25B0%258D%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%258F%2590%25E9%25AB%2598%25E6%2597%2585%25E8%25AD%25A6-%25E5%2588%2597%25E9%25AB%2598%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2588%2592-214500103.html&d=QE5rvD4iboeChbAAuj3apL%2FjevXO%2BySp3REELKrGah4%3D&h=565b6589\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%BE%B3%E6%B4%B2%E5%B0%8D%E6%B8%AF%E6%8F%90%E9%AB%98%E6%97%85%E8%AD%A6-%E5%88%97%E9%AB%98%E5%BA%A6%E8%AD%A6%E6%88%92-214500103.html</a><br />\n<br />\n【本報綜合報道】香港政府修訂《逃犯條例》風波觸發連串遊行衝突。澳洲外交及貿易部周二提高旅遊警示，將香港的旅遊安全級別列為「高度警戒」（High degree of caution）級別，呼籲國民訪港期間避免參與大型公眾活動，注意人身安全，及遵循港府指示。<br />\n<br />\n籲國民避開大型公眾集會<br />\n<br />\n澳洲外交及貿易部指出，香港示威活動變得更加不可預測，預料情況將持續一段時間，令旅遊區也受影響。示威人士、警察或有犯罪背景人士之間，存有暴力衝突的風險，尤其是在未經授權的抗議活動；當中在夜間和周末的風險更大，因此強烈建議國民避免大型公眾集會。<br />\n<br />\n澳洲外長佩恩在社交網上指出，澳洲對香港近日不斷增加的連串暴力事件，及對旅遊和住宅區造成的影響表示十分關注。她指和平抗議權利是基本法一部分，敦促各方和平解決紛爭，並且繼續支持香港「一國兩制」模式。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />口外部出黎譴責澳洲啦<br />\n快D唔准人去澳沖<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"920977b9a154b0dc1ba118b0dc71ce1fdc41c6fb","tid":1426247,"uid":226974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T01:36:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>傳來賀電</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}